<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1634408-does-the-book--series-have-simple">Does the book- series have simple languange-vocabulary? I&#39;m planning on reading it in english although it&#39;s not my native language.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1634408'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F13890.A_Crown_of_Swords">like</a></span>

